Standards-Version: 4.7.2

Package: openmediavault-snapraid-aio
Architecture: all
Depends: bc,
         curl,
         jq,
         openmediavault (>= 8),
         python3-markdown,
         snapraid (>= 12)
Description: SnapRAID AIO plugin for OpenMediaVault
 Integrates the SnapRAID AIO Script into the OpenMediaVault web interface.
 Provides per-array configuration, scheduled sync/scrub via the OMV cron
 system, email and Apprise notifications, Docker container management, and
 live output streaming for manual runs directly from the UI.
